==English==
===Noun phrase===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[w:Coulomb|Coulomb's]] [[law]]'''
#{{physics}} the [[fundamental]] law of [[electrostatics]] - the [[force]] between two [[point]] [[charge]]s is [[proportional]] to the [[product]] of their charges, and [[inversely]] proportional to the [[square]] of the [[distance]] between them

